snippet.title: DevGAMM
snippet.description:
DevGAMM is the biggest game developers conference in Eastern Europe. DevGAMM gives gaming experts a chance to keep up with the latest thinking and developments in making games as well as share their knowledge and experience with each other.

Every week we share talks and other sessions from DevGAMM events on this channel. The videos cover a wide range of gamedev-related topics: game design, marketing, indie development, game engines, art, graphics, animation and more!

Come, take a look. We are glad to have you 🙂
